Uses of Package
org.cloudbus.cloudsim.distributions

  • Packages that use org.cloudbus.cloudsim.distributions 
    Package Description
    org.cloudbus.cloudsim.distributions
    Provides Pseudo Random Number Generators (PRNG) following several statistical distributions used by the simulation API.
    org.cloudbus.cloudsim.resources
    Provides classes that represent different physical and logical Resource used by simulation objects such as Hosts and VMs.
    org.cloudsimplus.heuristics
    Provides a set of interfaces and classes to develop heuristics to find sub-optimal solutions for problems, considering some utility function that has to be minimized or maximized.
  • Classes in org.cloudbus.cloudsim.distributions used by org.cloudbus.cloudsim.distributions 
    Class and Description
    ContinuousDistribution
    Interface to be implemented by a pseudo random number generator.
    ContinuousDistributionAbstract
    An base class for implementation of ContinuousDistributions.
    ParetoDistr
    A pseudo random number generator following the Pareto distribution.
    UniformDistr
    A pseudo random number generator following the Uniform continuous distribution.
  • Classes in org.cloudbus.cloudsim.distributions used by org.cloudbus.cloudsim.resources 
    Class and Description
    ContinuousDistribution
    Interface to be implemented by a pseudo random number generator.
  • Classes in org.cloudbus.cloudsim.distributions used by org.cloudsimplus.heuristics 
    Class and Description
    ContinuousDistribution
    Interface to be implemented by a pseudo random number generator.
